invalid type: string "TABOO: Touching, Standing On, or Damaging Marine Coral Reefs\n\nStepping on live coral structures while snorkeling or diving in protected zones like Menjangan Island or Nusa Penida.\n\nRationale: Breaks local conservation protocols and severely damages fragile marine ecosystems that coastal villages rely on for protection.", expected f64ng Bali into spiritual ’L’’’’’’’’’’’’